chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to go?
yes
alright, buddy
i'm at the starting point and i see a twig to the left leading to a small island with a tiger on it. where to next?
go towards the parrot
got it! i'm off to the big island with the parrot
what's next?
going around the parrot passed the elephant you'll see rocks to cross towards the next island where you'll see a frog
gotcha, mate! so, passing by the parrot and the elephant, crossing these rocks to the island with the frog
alright! what's next?
move forward crossing the aligator and the rock towards the next island where you'll see the giraffe
roger that! crossing past the crocodile and heading to the giraffe now
what's next, boss?
from the giraffe, you'll cross towards the snack using the stick and grab the chest with gold. You're done!
thanks, bud! found the snake, moved past it and grabbed the treasure
we're done! *finished*
hola, q tal? ready to go?
yes!
alright, let's start! from where you stand next to the white dog, take a few steps left, walking towards a wooden bench
there, you'll see a trail that leads to a florist stand, but don't go all the way there – we're going to make a u-turn just before reaching it. got it?
ok done
good job! now cross the same trail and head back to the white dog
you'll see the bench again on your way
yes, see it
great, cross over the branch southwards
keep moving down until you find another white dog near a picnic. let me know when you get there
found it!
sweet! now go over the picnic mat and continue heading west till you see a bowl of berries
you're doing great so far!
got it
awesome! now, heads up, a river is coming up
you'll see a wooden branch we need to cross, it will lead us to the other side, northwards. on it!
got it, i crossed it
nice one! now, we need to sneak around a green bush without touching it
so, circle it from the right side till you reach a florist stand. should be no problem!
at the stand
perfect! now let's go a bit left, we're heading under the stand until we reach a massive bridge, watch out for the cyclists! let me know when you're at the bridge
at the bridge
good job! now, go past the bridge, just a bit to the west
passed it
perfect! you should see two seniors enjoying their newspapers
walk few steps south between them and a wooden branch. you got this!
made it
fantastic! you should see a green bush next to the end of that wooden branch, right? continue walking east, between the bush and the branch
keep me posted!
here
great! now just go a few steps east and
voila! you've arrived. see a young brown deer? congratulations!
hey, estas listo?
yes!
sweet! so i'm at the tent up north
where to first, buddy?
go passed the bush where the dog without touching the bush
ok, managed to pass the dog without disturbing the bush
now at the fire. what's next, mate?
make a right and go above the fire without touching it and stop at the mushrooms
made it to the mushrooms, without becoming a barbecue
what's my next move?
passed the mushrooms go a few steps towards the car, don't get too close
got it
steering clear of the car, but it's in my sights. what's next on our roadtrip, buddy?
go left, but a little downwards towards the bush next to the telescope, don't touch the bush and take the shortcut off the trial to get to the telescope
gotcha, staying the course, just passed the bush
at the telescope now!
go left a coiple steps until you see some rocks, go northwest towards the house going through the house and you make it!
sounds like a plan, hold on
alright, navigated through the rocks, and hey, there's the house! *finished* thanks for the directions, mate, couldn't have done it without ya!
hola, q tal? ready to play?
yes
great! you're at the three palm trees, right? head southwest under the first one, then make a right
pass the second tree and take a sharp left before the third. keep moving south
ok
perfect! now, can you see a cute brown puppy? navigate left of it, slight turn to the left then go right south
onwards!
got it
awesome! coming next you'll see a big rock on your left and a small rock on your right
cruise between 'em and you'll hit the water
yes got it
time for a swim! jump into the water and say hello to the red crab
then turn right heading along the big rock. you're almost there!
got it
great job! now, you'll encounter a medium rock
continue along it until you see a shark. don't worry, it's friendly! take a sharp right here
got it
alright! let's get back on land
navigate between the medium rock and the blue-yellow-white ball. keep going north
got it
nice! now turn slightly left and head northwest
there's a red tent and a big speaker ahead
got it
cool! now, you're going to arc around that tent, so make it like a nice half circle around it!
got it
superb! next, head south towards the sea
just before you hit the water, turn right and go under the red kayak. stay sharp!
got it
awesome! now, turn north, move along the kayak until you reach a small green bush
